131
00:08:07,321 --> 00:08:08,280
Tu veux une frite ?

132
00:08:08,363 --> 00:08:10,240
Oh oui !

133
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:15,413
C'était Billy Joel.

134
00:08:15,496 --> 00:08:18,415
On ne change pas de poste
quand c'est Billy Joel.

135
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:43,023
Papa ?

136
00:08:43,106 --> 00:08:44,191
Je peux pas respirer !

137
00:08:44,274 --> 00:08:47,111
Papa, ça va ? Papa !

138
00:08:47,194 --> 00:08:49,947
Papa !

139
